      "content": "but what if walking through the dark just makes you more tired? i'm so tired. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. it's like i'm living a life that's already finished. i look at everything we built together and it feels like a museum of a person who doesn't exist anymore. why should i keep walking when there's nowhere left to go?",
